text: Tribhuwana Wijayatunggadewi was the third ruler and Rajaputri/Queen of Majapahit who reigned from 1328-1351. She was the half sister of king Jayanegara. From since 1351 it is known that his abhiseka Sri Tribhuwana Wijayatunggadewi Maharajasa Jayawisnuwardhani.
